.croatia.org/crown/articles/10480/1/Lorde-an-authentic-new-music-star-on-a-horizon.html|title=Lorde an authentic new music star on a horizon|work=Croatia.org|date=2013-05-11|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417053705/http://www.croatia.org/crown/articles/10480/1/Lorde-an-authentic-new-music-star-on-a-horizon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/lorde-by-royal-appointment-1.1632966|title=Lorde - by royal appointment|work=Irish Times|date=2013-12-20|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217075039/https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/lorde-by-royal-appointment-1.1632966|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="vevolift">{{cite interview |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vt4OeI3Q6gk |title=Lorde — Beginnings (VEVO LIFT): Brought To You By McDonald's |accessdate=2014-04-21 |subject=Lorde |interviewer=VEVO |date=2013-10-07 |publisher=VEVO |archive-date=2021-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220034841/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vt4OeI3Q6gk |dead-url=no }}</ref>她在奥克兰郊区的{{link-en|德文波特 (新西兰)|Devonport, Auckland|德文波特}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10880718|date=2013-05-02|title=Lorde: Behind the success story|work=The New Zealand Herald|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328073025/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10880718|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="coupdemain">{{cite web|url=http://www.coupdemainmagazine.com/interviews/interview-inside-mind-lorde|title=Inside The Mind Of... Lorde|date=2013-03-20|author=Shahlin Graves|publisher=Coup De Main|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407153947/https://www.coupdemainmagazine.com/interviews/interview-inside-mind-lorde|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="first"/><ref name="cover"/>与姐姐杰瑞（{{lang|en|Jerry}}）、弟弟安杰罗（{{lang|en|Angelo}}）和妹妹英蒂亚（{{lang|en|India}}）一起长大。<ref name="wwd080913">{{cite web| url=http://www.wwd.com/eye/people/teen-queen-lorde-takes-new-york-7084070| title=Teen Queen: Lorde Takes New York| work=Women's Wear Daily| date=2013-08-09| author=McCarthy, Lauren| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2016-05-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527054602/http://wwd.com/eye/people/teen-queen-lorde-takes-new-york-7084070/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/9208190/Our-Lady-Lorde-The-Kiwi-schoolgirl-turned-pop-Royalty| title=Our Lady Lorde: The Kiwi schoolgirl turned pop Royalty| publisher=Stuff.co.nz| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2021-02-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220034912/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/9208190/Our-Lady-Lorde-The-Kiwi-schoolgirl-turned-pop-Royalty| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lorde's little sis releases song|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/9632728/Lordes-little-sis-releases-song|newspaper=Stuff|date=2014-01-21|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209071142/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/9632728/Lordes-little-sis-releases-song|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她持有新西兰与克罗地亚公民身份。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedubrovniktimes.com/news/croatia/item/3053-lorde-reveals-that-she-has-croatian-citizenship|title=Lorde reveals that she has Croatian citizenship|date=2017-09-08|work=The Dubrovnik Times|accessdate=2017-09-09|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220034817/https://www.thedubrovniktimes.com/news/croatia/item/3053-lorde-reveals-that-she-has-croatian-citizenship|dead-url=no}}</ref>

洛德在5岁时和朋友一起加入了学校的戏剧社团，从此发现自己对演唱和表演的热爱。<ref name=RollingStoneMe5Nov2013>{{cite web| url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lordes-teenage-dream-20131028| title=Lorde's Teenage Dream| date=2013-10-28| author=Jonah Weiner| work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2018-06-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629074456/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lordes-teenage-dream-20131028| dead-url=no}}</ref>她表示十分享受在表演时“展现自己的另一面，成为另一个不同的自己”的过程。<ref name=telegraph1>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/10433978/Lorde-interview-Dream-Teen.html|title=Lorde interview: Dream Teen|author=Bernadette McNulty|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2013-11-08|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217075136/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/10433978/Lorde-interview-Dream-Teen.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在自己诗人母亲的鼓励下，她阅读了大量书籍，养成了安静的性格，但在表演时也能自如地在公众面前发言。<ref name=RollingStoneMe5Nov2013 /><ref name=telegraph1 />

洛德曾就读于{{link-en|贝尔蒙特预科学校|Belmont Intermediate School}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/auckland/local-news/north-shore-times/8990736/Singer-now-on-centre-stage|title=Singer now on centre stage: Shore kid makes good at Splendour in the Grass|date=2013-08-02|first=Jess|last=Etheridge|work=North Shore Times|publisher=Stuff.co.nz|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053757/http://www.stuff.co.nz/auckland/local-news/north-shore-times/8990736/Singer-now-on-centre-stage|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年在校期间，她和朋友路易斯·麦克唐纳（{{lang|en|Louis McDonald}}）共同参加了学校的才艺比赛，演唱了[[黛菲|黛菲]]的〈{{link-en|沃里克大道|Warwick Avenue (song)}}〉和[[皮克西·洛特|皮克西·洛特]]的〈{{link-en|妈妈会怎样|Mama Do (Uh Oh, Uh Oh)}}〉两首歌曲，并赢得学校才艺比赛的冠军。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/lorde-returns-to-belmont-intermediate-school-to-judge-talent-show/story-fni0b8dw-1226761816655 |title=Lorde returns to Belmont Intermediate School to judge talent show |work=Herald Sun |date=2013-11-17 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2019-02-16 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/76Dfyut0H?url=https://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/lorde-returns-to-belmont-intermediate-school-to-judge-talent-show/news-story/fd9f2d49397cd63a45031e9f245da8e8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>麦克唐纳的父亲看到洛德在比赛中的表演之后，把她翻唱这两首歌曲的录像发给了几位[[星探|星探]]。<ref name="telegraph1"/>洛德13岁时，[[A&R|A&R]]人员斯科特·麦克拉克兰（{{lang|en|Scott Maclachlan}}）看到这段录像之后将她签约至[[环球唱片|环球唱片]]旗下，开启了她创作歌手的生涯，但事业之初并未获得成功。<ref name="hitquarters.com"/><ref name="Stuff.co.NZ:newestPop">{{cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/culture/performance/8654143/Lorde-NZs-newest-pop-star|title=NZ newest pop star|date=2013-05-10|last=White|first=Caitlin|publisher=Tom Cardy|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2018-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925042037/http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/culture/performance/8654143/Lorde-NZs-newest-pop-star|dead-url=no}}</ref>麦克拉克兰在接受音乐媒体{{link-en|HitQuarters|HitQuarters}}采访时表示：“……她（指洛德）明白要创作属于自己的音乐，但是在制作方面还是需要有人来帮她。”<ref name="hitquarters.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/opar/intrview_ScottM.html |title=Interview with Scott MacLachlan |publisher=HitQuarters |date=2014-01-21 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202112135/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2Fopar%2Fintrview_ScottM.html |archivedate=2014-02-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>也正是在这一段时间，即十二三岁左右时，洛德开始用吉他创作自己的歌曲。她最终与词曲作者兼制作人{{link-en|乔尔·利特|Joel Little}}展开合作。二人的合作“十分合拍”，在一周之内便创作出包括〈贵族〉在内的三首歌曲。<ref name="hitquarters.com"/>

==職業生涯==

===2012－2015年：《纯粹女英雄》及《饥饿游戏》原声带===
2012年11月，洛德发行了首张[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《{{link-en|愛之俱樂部|The Love Club}}》，在[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]提供免费下载。<ref name="cover"/><ref name="hitquarters.com"/>她的经纪人麦克拉克兰表示：“我们感觉这是一张非常强大的音乐思想作品，所以就想先把它发行出来吧，以后再考虑钱的问题…… 但是下载超过了60,000次之后，（唱片公司说）我们不能这样继续（免费提供下载）了。”<ref name="hitquarters.com"/>一位美国音乐总监，娜塔莉亚·罗米佐斯基（{{lang|en|Natalia Romiszewski}}）听到这张迷你专辑之后，把它推荐给了环球唱片旗下子公司{{link-en|Lava唱片|Lava Records}}的-{zh-hans:首席执行官;zh-hant:執行長;zh-cn:首席执行官;zh-hk:行政總裁;zh-tw:執行長;zh-mo:行政總裁;}-{{link-en|杰森·弗洛姆|Jason Flom}}。弗洛姆听过后决定与洛德本人见面，并将她签约至自己的公司。<ref name="hitquarters.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1568730/lorde-breaks-onto-us-charts-preps-september-album|work=Billboard|date=2013-07-01|title=Lorde Breaks Onto U.S. Charts, Preps September Album|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217075205/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1568730/lorde-breaks-onto-us-charts-preps-september-album|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后专辑中的歌曲〈贵族〉在[[Spotify|Spotify]]上迅速成名，弗洛姆称：“……全世界立刻就给出热烈反响……（〈贵族〉）这首歌就是一个火花，点燃了全球的活跃瞩目，最终也推动了洛德出色的首张专辑的发行。”<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/stevenbertoni/2013/11/26/how-spotify-made-lorde-a-pop-superstar/|title=How Spotify Made Lorde A Pop Superstar|work=Forbes|date=2013-11-26|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220034918/https://www.forbes.com/sites/stevenbertoni/2013/11/26/how-spotify-made-lorde-a-pop-superstar/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《愛之俱樂部》这张迷你专辑于2013年3月正式发行[[数字音乐下载|数字下载]]版本，5月正式发行[[CD|CD]]版本，收录了五首歌曲，其中包括冠军单曲〈[[贵族_(歌曲)|贵族]]〉。〈贵族〉于2013年3月作为单曲正式发行，一经发行即登上[[新西兰单曲排行榜|新西兰单曲排行榜]]冠军，并在这一位置保持了三周。<ref name="royals-nz-chart">{{cite web|url=http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Royals&cat=s|title=Lorde – Royals|work=Charts.org.nz|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604055335/http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Royals&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年6月，单曲〈贵族〉在美国正式发行，首周销量即高达85,000份。<ref name="Iain">{{cite news|title=Lorde's calling delivers her to splendour|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/arts/music/lords-calling-delivers-her-to-splendour/story-fn9d2mxu-1226687182632?utm_source=The%20Australian&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=editorial&net_sub_uid=44933799|accessdate=2014-04-21|newspaper=The Australian|date=2013-07-29|author=Iain Sheddon|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106101059/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/arts/music/lords-calling-delivers-her-to-splendour/story-fn9d2mxu-1226687182632?utm_source=The%20Australian&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=editorial&net_sub_uid=44933799|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月，这支单曲登上了美国[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]另类单曲榜冠军，使洛德成为继1996年之后17年来首位在这一排行榜获得冠军单曲的女性艺人。<ref name="first">{{cite web|title=Lorde First Woman in 17 Years to Top Alternative with 'Royals'|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/global/5646336/lorde-first-woman-in-17-years-to-top-alternative-with-royals|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2014-04-21|date=2013-08-16|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328061113/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/global/5646336/lorde-first-woman-in-17-years-to-top-alternative-with-royals|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈贵族〉后来还登上[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]冠军位置，并保持了九周之久；在告示牌摇滚单曲榜也获得了冠军。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/5755397/lorde-haim-bring-girl-power-to-alternative |title=Lorde, HAIM Bring Girl Power To Alternative |work=Billboard |date=2013-10-11 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2015-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913201812/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/5755397/lorde-haim-bring-girl-power-to-alternative |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5800854/lorde-royals-hot-100-chart-nine-weeks-eminem|title=Lorde's 'Royals' Rules Hot 100 For Ninth Week|work=Billboard|date=2013-11-27|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207115359/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5800854/lorde-royals-hot-100-chart-nine-weeks-eminem|dead-url=no}}</ref>洛德也因此成为首位获得告示牌百强单曲榜冠军单曲的新西兰独唱艺人。<ref name=abc>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-10-03/lorde-becomes-first-kiwi-solo-artist-to-top-us-billboard-chart/4996368 |title=Lorde's Royals becomes first track from New Zealand solo artist to top US Billboard chart |publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2013-10-03 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2021-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220034958/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-10-03/lorde-becomes-first-kiwi-solo-artist-to-top-us-billboard-chart/4996368 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而这支单曲登顶告示牌百强单曲榜时，她年龄尚不满17岁，也因此成为1987年以来的26年内最年轻的告示牌冠军单曲获得者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/04/lorde-is-youngest-performer-to-top-billboard-charts-in-26-years/|title=Lorde is Youngest Performer to Top Billboard Charts in 26 Years|work=Time|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004164716/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/04/lorde-is-youngest-performer-to-top-billboard-charts-in-26-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5740767/lordes-royals-crowns-hot-100|title=Lorde's 'Royals' Crowns Hot 100|work=Billboard|date=2013-10-02|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330184844/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5740767/lordes-royals-crowns-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>

