2013年6月8日，洛德在新西兰发行了第二张迷你专辑《网球场》（{{lang|en|''Tennis Court EP''}}）的数字下载版，在英国因时差原因则于6月7日发行。<ref name="Tennis Court-iTunes">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/nz/album/tennis-court-single/id657273441|title=Tennis Court – Single by Lorde|work=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (NZ)|publisher=[[Apple_Inc|Apple Inc]]|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009010239/https://itunes.apple.com/nz/album/tennis-court-single/id657273441|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/tennis-court-ep/id657273465|title=Tennis Court – EP by Lorde|work=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (UK)|publisher=[[Apple_Inc|Apple Inc]]|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009064047/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/tennis-court-ep/id657273465|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月22日，这张迷你专辑的实体版开始发售。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theleftoversessions.co.uk/2013/06/06/lorde-tennis-court-ep/|title=Lorde: 'Tennis Court' EP|author=Mary|publisher=The Leftover Sessions|date=2013-06-06|accessdate=2014-04-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021095234/http://theleftoversessions.co.uk/2013/06/06/lorde-tennis-court-ep/|archivedate=2013-10-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/release/mr0003987647|work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]|accessdate=2014-04-17|title=Lorde: Tennis Court|archive-date=2017-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126151518/https://www.allmusic.com/album/release/mr0003987647|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年6月14日，其中的单曲〈[[网球场_(歌曲)|网球场]]〉登上新西兰单曲榜的首位，而洛德也同时成为首个同时有四支单曲进入新西兰单曲榜前20位的艺人。<ref name="tennis-court-nz-chart">{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=2215|title=Lorde – Tennis Court|publisher=nztop40.co.nz|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019094506/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=2215|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年7月，洛德还代替因病缺席的[[弗兰克·奥申|弗兰克·奥申]]参加了澳洲“{{lang|en|Splendour in the Grass}}”音乐节的表演。<ref name="Iain" />

2013年8月12日，洛德通过[[Twitter|Twitter]]宣布自己将于9月30日在美国发行个人首张专辑《[[天生英雌|天生英雌]]》。<ref name="Debut">{{cite web|title=Lorde Announces Debut Album 'Pure Heroine'|url=http://thecorner.co.nz/2013/08/13/lorde-announces-debut-album-pure-heroine/|work=The Corner|author=Hussein Moses|date=2013-08-13|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917162153/http://thecorner.co.nz/2013/08/13/lorde-announces-debut-album-pure-heroine/|archive-date=2013-09-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>专辑发行后获得评论界的广泛好评。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/pure-heroine/lorde|title=Pure Heroine - Lorde|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004044906/http://www.metacritic.com/music/pure-heroine/lorde|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/5733177/lorde-pure-heroine-track-by-track-review|title=Lorde, 'Pure Heroine': Track-By-Track Review|work=Billboard|date=2013-09-25|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6MNBwPdKZ?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/5733177/lorde-pure-heroine-track-by-track-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/pure-heroine-20131007|title=Lorde Pure Heroine|work=[[滚石_(杂志)|Rolling Stone]]|date=2013-10-07|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721055913/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/pure-heroine-20131007|dead-url=no}}</ref>一经发售即登上新西兰专辑排行榜冠军位置，首周销量即达到[[音乐唱片销售认证|白金唱片认证]]，并连续保持两周冠军。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lorde's Pure Heroine goes #1, platinum in first week|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11134905|work=The New Zealand Herald|publisher=APN News & Media|accessdate=2014-04-21|date=2013-10-05|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918082013/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11134905|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2297 |title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart |publisher=The Official New Zealand Music Chart |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012030642/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2297 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2304 |title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart |publisher=The Official New Zealand Music Chart |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2013-10-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131018050812/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2014年3月，专辑已经获得新西兰唱片业协会的四白金销量认证。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2409 |title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart |publisher=The Official New Zealand Music Chart |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209053059/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2409 |dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑在澳大利亚也登上了专辑榜冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Pure+Heroine&cat=a|title=LORDE - PURE HEROINE (ALBUM)|work=Australiancharts.com|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217081157/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Pure+Heroine&cat=a|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在美国，专辑发行首周销量高达129,000张，登上[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]第三位，随后于2014年2月获得了[[美国唱片业协会|美国唱片业协会]]的白金唱片认证。<ref name=200entry>{{cite news| url= http://billboard.com/articles/news/5748190/justin-timberlake-scores-his-second-no-1-album-of-2013| title= Justin Timberlake Scores His Second No. 1 Album Of 2013| first= Keith| last= Caulfield| location= Los Angeles| work= Billboard| date= 2013-10-09| accessdate= 2014-04-21| archive-date= 2014-03-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140330221052/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5748190/justin-timberlake-scores-his-second-no-1-album-of-2013| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?artist=%22Pure+Heroine%22|title=American album certifications – Lorde – Pure Heroine|work=[[美国唱片业协会|RIAA]]|accessdate=2014-04-21}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>根据[[国际唱片业协会|国际唱片业协会]]数据，截至2013年底，专辑在全球已售出逾150万张。<ref>{{cite web|title=2013 Annual Report – Section 4.2 Commentaires sur les performances opérationnelles des métiers|url=http://www.vivendi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/20140225_Rapport_financier_et_Etats_financiers_consolides_audites_de_l-exercice_2013.pdf|publisher=Vivendi. Compagnie Générale des Eaux|accessdate=2014-04-21|format=PDF|page=22|language=fr|archive-date=2014-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140513175739/http://www.vivendi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/20140225_Rapport_financier_et_Etats_financiers_consolides_audites_de_l-exercice_2013.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>而洛德也凭借这张专辑获得众多音乐奖项。

