m/articles/news/6049353/nirvana-joined-by-joan-jett-kim-gordon-st-vincent-lorde-at-rock-hall-ceremony|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月又登上了加拿大{{le|iHeartRadio Much 音乐录影带大奖|iHeartRadio Much Music Video Awards}}的舞台，表演了〈[[团队_(歌曲)|团队]]〉和〈[[网球场_(歌曲)|网球场]]〉两首歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|title=MMVAs: Lorde (and Her Lamp) Rule The 2014 MuchMusic Video Awards|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2014/06/15/mmvas-2014-winners-performers-photos_n_5497420.html|publisher=Huffington Post|accessdate=2016-08-11|date=2014-06-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065946/http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2014/06/15/mmvas-2014-winners-performers-photos_n_5497420.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

