2013年12月，洛德宣布已经开始创作第二张录音室专辑所需的素材。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5833529/lorde-working-on-new-material-tour-down-under-on-the-cards |title=Lorde Working on New Material, Australian Tour Being Planned |work=Billboard |date=2013-12-13 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2014-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704082410/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5833529/lorde-working-on-new-material-tour-down-under-on-the-cards |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年6月，她表示第二张专辑已经开始前期制作，目前为止与第一张专辑“完全不同”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a575623/lorde-my-next-album-will-sound-totally-different.html |title=Lorde: 'My next album will sound totally different' |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |date=2014-06-05 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829072621/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a575623/lorde-my-next-album-will-sound-totally-different.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年8月，专辑已进入后期制作。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lorde's Second Album is Nearing Completion: 'We're in the Production Stage Now'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7487084/lorde-new-album-production-stage|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=2016-08-30|date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217075649/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7487084/lorde-new-album-production-stage|dead-url=no}}</ref>次年2月，洛德发布了全新的音乐录影带预告片。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Britton|first1=Luke Morgan|title=Watch Lorde tease new music in mysterious adverts - NME|url=http://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lorde-tease-new-music-album-advert-1994979|website=NME|accessdate=2017-03-02|date=2017-02-27|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035348/https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lorde-tease-new-music-album-advert-1994979|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月3日，她发行了新专辑首支单曲〈{{le|绿光 (洛德歌曲)|Green Light (Lorde song)|绿光}}〉，<ref name="p4k melodrama">{{cite web|title=Lorde announces second album 'Melodrama' - NME|url=http://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-announces-second-album-melodrama-1999456|website=NME|accessdate=2017-03-03|date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2022-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101014107/https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-announces-second-album-melodrama-1999456|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lorde Announces New Album Melodrama {{!}} Pitchfork|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/68373-lorde-announces-new-album-melodrama/|publisher=Pitchfork|date=2017-03-03|accessdate=2017-03-03|archive-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302211854/http://pitchfork.com/news/68373-lorde-announces-new-album-melodrama|dead-url=no}}</ref>于3月11日在美国综艺节目《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》首次表演这首歌曲，<ref>{{cite web|last1=Romaine|first1=Jenna|title=March Episodes of 'SNL' to Feature Father John Misty & Lorde as Musical Guests|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/television/7701879/saturday-night-live-father-john-misty-lorde-musical-guests|website=Billboard|accessdate=2017-03-02|date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035500/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/television/7701879/saturday-night-live-father-john-misty-lorde-musical-guests|dead-url=no}}</ref>还参加了当年[[科切拉音乐节|科切拉音乐节]]的表演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7646975/2017-lorde-new-album-coachella-governors-ball|title=2017 Will Be the Year of Our Lorde|publisher=Billboard|date=2017-01-04|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035408/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7646975/2017-lorde-new-album-coachella-governors-ball|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年6月16日，洛德通过[[聯眾唱片|聯眾唱片]]正式发布新专辑《[[狂想曲_(蘿兒專輯)|狂想曲]]》。她在专辑中与[[傑克·安多夫|傑克·安多夫]]、[[托芙蘿|托芙蘿]]、[[喬爾·立特|喬爾·立特]]等艺人合作，本人参与了全部歌曲的创作。<ref name="p4k melodrama"/>专辑一经发行即获得广泛好评，《[[新音乐快递|新音乐快递]]》、《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》、[[Pitchfork|Pitchfork]]等乐评媒体都给出了满分或高分评价。<ref>{{cite web|title=Melodrama by Lorde|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/melodrama/lorde|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2017-06-17|archive-date=2017-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170715054021/http://www.metacritic.com/music/melodrama/lorde|dead-url=no}}</ref>这张专辑在新西兰<ref>{{cite web|title=charts.org.nz - Lorde - Melodrama|url=http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Melodrama&cat=a|website=charts.org.nz|accessdate=2017-08-09|archive-date=2018-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127024657/http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Melodrama&cat=a|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、澳大利亚<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hung|first1=Steffen|title=australian-charts.com - Lorde - Melodrama|url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Melodrama&cat=a|website=australian-charts.com|accessdate=2017-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035427/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lorde&titel=Melodrama&cat=a|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美国<ref name="US200"/>和加拿大<ref name= CANalbums/>获得专辑榜冠军。音乐媒体《新音乐快递》和[[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]]都将其评为2017年度专辑第一名。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nme.com/list/nmes-albums-of-the-year-2017-2161481|title=NME’s Albums of The Year 2017|publisher=NME|date=2017-11-23|accessdate=2017-11-23|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130012957/http://www.nme.com/list/nmes-albums-of-the-year-2017-2161481|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/99197037/Lorde-scoops-prestigious-UK-music-mags-album-of-the-year-award-with-Melodrama|title=Lorde scoops prestigious UK music mag's album of the year award with 'Melodrama'|publisher=Stuff.co.nz|date=2017-11-23|accessdate=2017-11-23|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035529/https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/99197037/lorde-scoops-prestigious-uk-music-mags-album-of-the-year-award-with-melodrama|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2017/11/top-50-albums-of-2017/5/|title=Top 50 Albums of 2017|publisher=Consequence of Sound|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-11-27|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201041220/https://consequenceofsound.net/2017/11/top-50-albums-of-2017/5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这张专辑还获得[[第60届格莱美奖|第60届格莱美奖]]年度专辑的提名。<ref name="2018Grammy">{{cite web|title=Grammys 2018 Winners: The Complete List|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/grammys/8096569/grammys-2018-winners-list|website=Billboard|accessdate=2018-01-30|date=2018-01-28|archive-date=2018-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208204548/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/grammys/8096569/grammys-2018-winners-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2021年 - 至今：《日光》===
2021年6月11日，無預警發布單曲〈[[日光_(歌曲)|日光]]〉，成為她睽違四年的第一張單曲，空降告示牌第六十四名，英國則獲得第十七名。隨後，她宣布第三張錄音室專輯《[[日光_(專輯)|日光]]》將在8月20日釋出，以及在2022年將展開的「{{lang|en|Solar Power Tour}}」。

==艺术特色==
===声音和音乐===
洛德称自己会着重关注自己的声音，表示“我不演奏乐器，所以会重点关注自己的声音。我的音色真的很重要。”<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |url=http://noisey.vice.com/blog/meet-lorde-shes-a-talented-teenage-badass |title=Meet Lorde: She's a Talented Teenage Badass | NOISEY |publisher=Noisey.vice.com |date=2013-06-27 |accessdate=2013-12-16 |archive-date=2013-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028031927/http://noisey.vice.com/blog/meet-lorde-shes-a-talented-teenage-badass |dead-url=no }}</ref>她在演唱时多使用[[美国英语|美国口音]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/culture/9217394/Review-Lordes-Pure-Heroine |title=Review: Lorde's Pure Heroine |first=Tom |last=Cardy |work=The Dominion Post |publisher=Fairfax New Zealand |date=2013-09-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NjeRBEEF?url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/culture/9217394/Review-Lordes-Pure-Heroine |archivedate=2014-02-28 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]形容她的音乐风格“混合了一种带有艺术气质和自白忏悔的卧室流行风格以及另一种夜店的电子摇滚风格”，并把她与{{link-en|Grimes|Grimes (musician)}}、[[拉娜·德雷|拉娜·德雷]]和{{link-en|斯凯·费雷拉|Sky Ferreira}}等艺人相比较。<ref name="AllMusic-Genre">{{cite web |author=Artist Biography by James Christopher Monger |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/lorde-mn0003085111/biography |title=Lorde | Biography |publisher=AllMusic |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2021-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035637/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/lorde-mn0003085111/biography |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》乐评人詹姆斯·拉克诺（{{lang|en|James Lachno}}）称洛德的声音“错落起伏”而且“有潮流的电音特质”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|title=Lorde – New Music|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|first=James|last=Lachno|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131709/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而在歌词方面，《愛之俱樂部》和《纯粹女英雄》的歌词都是受到了她年轻时代生活的影响，表达了对主流文化的批判。<ref>{{cite web|last=Interrante|first=Scott|url=http://www.popmatters.com/post/175777-gold-teeth-white-teeth-and-lordes-pure-heroine/|title=Gold Teeth, White Teeth, and Lorde's 'Pure Heroine'|work=PopMatters|date=2013-10-10|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825223301/http://www.popmatters.com/post/175777-gold-teeth-white-teeth-and-lordes-pure-heroine/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite web |last=Ehrlich |first=Brenna |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1710775/lorde-royals.jhtml |title=Lorde: More 'Real' Than Bieber, Cooler Than You – Music, Celebrity, Artist News |publisher=MTV |date=2013-07-18 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2014-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423141403/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1710775/lorde-royals.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>《纯粹女英雄》专辑的歌词更是“在青春期的失落和焦虑的基础上”，<ref>{{cite web |author=Review by Stephen Thomas Erlewine |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/pure-heroine-mw0002574004 |title=Pure Heroine – Lorde | Songs, Reviews, Credits, Awards |publisher=AllMusic |date=2013-09-30 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701235843/http://www.allmusic.com/album/pure-heroine-mw0002574004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以冷眼旁观的怪诞视角“探索了传统[[少年流行曲|青春流行歌曲]]中的主题——[[社交恐懼症|社交焦虑]]、浪漫幻想、空虚衰弱和醉酒狂欢等等”。<ref>{{cite web |author=By Jonah Weiner |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lordes-teenage-dream-20131028 |title=Lorde: The Rise of Pop's Edgiest Teen | Music News |work=Rolling Stone |date=2013-10-28 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2018-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629074456/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lordes-teenage-dream-20131028 |dead-url=no }}</ref>例如〈贵族〉一曲中“我们不在乎，反正我們也不會介入你的桃色關係”（{{lang|en|We don't care, we aren't caught up in your love affair."}}）等歌词就强烈讽刺了当前的青春流行文化。<ref name="50 Best Albums">{{cite web| url= http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/50-best-albums-of-2013-20131202/lorde-pure-heroine-19691231| title= 50 Best Albums of 2013: Lorde, 'Pure Heroine'| work= [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]| accessdate= 2014-04-21| archive-date= 2018-06-29| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180629074232/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/50-best-albums-of-2013-20131202/lorde-pure-heroine-19691231| dead-url= no}}</ref>

===音乐影响===
洛德的音乐脱胎于[[流行電音|流行電音]]风格，但她却自幼接触[[伊特·珍|伊特·珍]]和[[奥蒂斯·雷丁|奥蒂斯·雷丁]]等人的灵魂音乐，以及她父母最爱的{{link-en|凯特·史蒂文斯|Cat Stevens}}、[[尼尔·杨|尼尔·杨]]和[[佛利伍麦克|佛利伍麦克]]等艺人。她称自己独特的声音特质是受到了{{link-en|Grimes|Grimes (musician)}}、{{link-en|Sleigh Bells|Sleigh Bells (band)|Sleigh Bells}}乐队和制作人{{link-en|SBTRKT|SBTRKT}}的突出影响。<ref>{{cite interview |subject=Lorde |interviewer=Lisa Kennedy Montgomery |title=Lorde In-Studio w/ Kennedy |date=2013-08-20 |publisher=KYSR |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e2y6H3MCqsk |at=2:58 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2013-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131127193156/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e2y6H3MCqsk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="James">{{cite news|title=Lorde – New Music|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|accessdate=2014-04-21|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2013-09-11|author=James Lachno|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131709/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>洛德还表示自己的一部分创作灵感是来自{{link-en|Burial|Burial (musician)}}和[[The_Weeknd|The Weeknd]]等艺人，还表示欣赏他们隐藏自己身份的行为，称自己“觉得保持神秘更有意思”。<ref name="cover">{{cite journal |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687161/lorde-the-billboard-cover-story |title=Lorde: The Billboard Cover Story |magazine=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |first=Jason |last=Lipshutz |issn=0006-2510 |date=2013-09-06 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |journal= |archive-date=2021-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031223911/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687161/lorde-the-billboard-cover-story |dead-url=no }}</ref>她还曾表示过自己对[[妮琪·米娜|妮琪·米娜]]的喜爱，称她是“流行音乐界的一位重要女性”，自己的音乐也受到了她的影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/09/13/facts-lorde/|title=Lorde: Five fast facts about the new alt music 'it' girl|last=Asare|first=Andrew|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-09-13|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102203925/http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/09/13/facts-lorde/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

洛德欣赏很多男性艺人，自己的音乐风格也受到他们的影响而包含了很多男性气质。她热爱{{link-en|詹姆斯·布雷克 (歌手)|James Blake (musician)|詹姆斯·布雷克}}的音乐，也吸收了他的风格影响；她还表示饶舌歌手[[J·科尔|J·科尔]]以及很多电子音乐制作人都为自己的创作提供了灵感。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vmusic.com.au/pages/main-menu/news/interviews/lorde-q-a |title=Lorde Q&A |publisher=VMusic |accessdate=2014-04-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408133117/http://www.vmusic.com.au/pages/main-menu/news/interviews/lorde-q-a |archivedate=2014-04-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/lorde-interview_n_3644831.html|title=Lorde, 16-Year-Old New Zealand Musician, Talks 'Royals' Video, Feminism And More|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://archive.is/20131014184950/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/lorde-interview_n_3644831.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在创作《愛之俱樂部》期间，她还特别受到了[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]的影响。<ref name=DigitalSpycoUKintimidatingPeers>{{cite web| url=http://DigitalSpy.co.UK/music/news/a529048/lorde-i-relate-to-kanye-west-and-i-feel-intimidated-by-teenage-girls.html| title=Lorde 'I relate to Kanye West and I feel intimidated by teenage girls' – Music News| date=2013-11-05| author=Leah Simpson| work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2013-11-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107225023/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a529048/lorde-i-relate-to-kanye-west-and-i-feel-intimidated-by-teenage-girls.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Pretty Much Amazing">{{cite web| last=Offitzer| first=Adam| url=http://prettymuchamazing.com/reviews/lorde-the-love-club-tennis-court| title=Review: Lorde – 'The Love Club' / 'Tennis Court'| publisher=Pretty Much Amazing| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2021-01-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111092522/http://prettymuchamazing.com/reviews/lorde-the-love-club-tennis-court/| dead-url=no}}</ref>除此之外，洛德还表示[[马文·盖伊|马文·盖伊]]、[[美好冬季樂團|美好冬季樂團]]、[[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]等艺人都对自己的音乐创作有很大影响。<ref name="influence"/><ref name=DigitalSpycoUKintimidatingPeers />

