==个人生活==
2013年，洛德在{{link-en|塔卡普纳文法学校|Takapuna Grammar School}}完成12年级的学业，并从该校毕业。<ref name="nzHerald.co.NZ:behindLorde">{{cite web| url=http://nzHerald.co.NZ/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10880718| title=Lorde: Behind the success story| date=2013-05-02| author=Charlotte Ryan| work=The New Zealand Herald| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2016-03-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328073025/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10880718| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://nzHerald.co.NZ/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10870642| title=Kiwi songbird with Universal appeal| date=2013-03-12| first1=James| last1=Ihaka| first2=Nicholas| last2=Jones| work=The New Zealand Herald| accessdate=2014-04-21| archive-date=2013-09-14| archive-url=https://archive.is/20130914190902/http://nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10870642| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/national/234418/she's-still-our-lorde,-say-friends |title=She's still our Lorde, say friends |publisher=Radio New Zealand National |date=2014-01-28 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2014-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313165451/http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/national/234418/she%27s-still-our-lorde%2C-say-friends |dead-url=no }}</ref>

洛德自认是一名“绝对全心全意的”[[女权主义者|女权主义者]]。<ref name="MetroArtsNZ:Sept2013" />她表示，女权主义完全没有什么值得惊奇的，只是“作为一个女孩天生的一部分”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/03/lorde-feminism-tavi-gevinson-rookie_n_4536018.html|title=Lorde: Feminism Is 'Completely Natural,' 'Just Part Of Being A Girl'|work=The Huffington Post|date=2014-01-03|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2017-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507232942/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/03/lorde-feminism-tavi-gevinson-rookie_n_4536018.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她曾因直言不讳批评其他艺人而引发巨大争议。她曾批评美國歌手[[賽琳娜·戈梅茲|賽琳娜·戈梅茲]]和[[拉娜·德雷|拉娜·德雷]]等人的歌词对女性缺乏尊重，不能给女性青少年以正确的引导，对她们歌词中塑造的女性形象表示不满。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gigwise.com/news/84574/feminist-lorde-slams-selena-gomez-single-come-and-get-it|title='Feminist' Lorde slams Selena Gomez single 'Come And Get It'|work=Gigwise|date=2013-09-29|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217080014/https://www.gigwise.com/news/84574/feminist-lorde-slams-selena-gomez-single-come-and-get-it|dead-url=no}}</ref>还曾公开表示反感美國歌手[[麦莉·赛勒斯|麦莉·赛勒斯]]在舞台表演时的过多性暗示；她称美國創作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]“高不可攀”，对青少年女孩没有起到积极作用等等。但随后她表示这些批评多是遭到了媒体的误读和渲染，自己对这些艺人本身并无攻击之意。之後和泰勒絲成為了好朋友。<ref name="MetroArtsNZ:Sept2013">{{cite news| url=http://MetroArts.co.NZ/music/lorde-storm-singer| title=Lorde: Storm Singer| date=2013-09-26| first1=Duncan| last1=Greive| publisher=Metro Arts Auckland|accessdate=2014-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023055643/http://metroarts.co.nz/music/lorde-storm-singer/|archivedate=2013-10-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bustle.com/articles/8347-why-the-confident-feminist-lorde-is-the-perfect-role-model-for-girls|title=WHY THE CONFIDENT, FEMINIST LORDE IS THE PERFECT ROLE MODEL FOR GIRLS|work=Bustle|date=2013-12|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217080022/https://www.bustle.com/articles/8347-why-the-confident-feminist-lorde-is-the-perfect-role-model-for-girls|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2558716/Lorde-insists-shes-not-anti-new-interview-dissing-Taylor-Miley.html|title=Singer Lorde, 17, insists she's not 'anti-anyone' in new interview... just months after dissing Taylor Swift and Miley Cyrus for their sexy images|work=Daily Mail|date=2014-02-13|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111092608/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2558716/Lorde-insists-shes-not-anti-new-interview-dissing-Taylor-Miley.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年末，媒体曝光了洛德与比她年长7岁的新西兰亚裔摄影师詹姆斯·洛韦（{{lang|en|James Lowe}}）的恋情。二人在她成名之前已经相识。<ref>{{cite web|title=James Lowe, Lorde's Boyfriend: 5 Fast Facts You Need To Know|url=http://www.heavy.com/entertainment/2013/12/who-is-lordes-boyfriend-james-lowe/|work=Heavy|accessdate=2014-04-21|author=Angela Barbuti|date=2013-12-12|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035727/https://heavy.com/entertainment/2013/12/who-is-lordes-boyfriend-james-lowe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>恋情公开后，二人一度因洛韦的亚裔身份和长相而受到网络上的大量语言攻击。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heavy.com/entertainment/2013/12/who-is-lordes-boyfriend-james-lowe/|title=James Lowe, Lorde’s Boyfriend: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|work=Heavy.com|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220035727/https://heavy.com/entertainment/2013/12/who-is-lordes-boyfriend-james-lowe/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/opinion/opinion-la/la-ol-lorde-asian-boyfriend-racist-comments-20131211,0,5546151.story#axzz2z7fY7Bmi|title=Dear Internet: Lorde is dating an Asian guy -- get over it|work=Los Angles Times|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426220010/http://www.latimes.com/opinion/opinion-la/la-ol-lorde-asian-boyfriend-racist-comments-20131211,0,5546151.story#axzz2z7fY7Bmi|dead-url=no}}</ref>二人之后在2015年末分手。<ref>{{cite web|title=Reports Lorde has split from boyfriend James Lowe|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11575510|publisher=NZ Herald|accessdate=2016-08-30|date=2016-01-18|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810124537/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11575510|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==慈善事业==
