==获奖与提名==
===格莱美奖===
[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]是由{{link-en|美国国立录音艺术科学学院|National Academy of Recording Arts and Sciences}}颁发的美国录音界和音乐界最重要的奖项。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.grammy.org/recording-academy/awards|title=The GRAMMY Awards|work=Grammy.org|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2013-01-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DkJje78f?url=http://www.grammy.org/recording-academy/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2014年的[[第56届格莱美奖|第56届格莱美奖]]上，洛德获得四项提名，其中包括凭借〈贵族〉获得的年度制作、最佳流行歌手、年度歌曲提名以及凭《纯粹女英雄》获得的最佳流行演唱专辑提名，<ref name="billboard1"/>并最终获得年度歌曲和最佳流行歌手两项大奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2546515/Grammy-Awards-2014-Lorde-rules-supreme-hit-Royals.html|title=Queen bee of cool Lorde, 17, rules supreme as she scoops two Grammy Awards and captivates on stage with her hit Royals|work=Daily Mail|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111093059/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2546515/Grammy-Awards-2014-Lorde-rules-supreme-hit-Royals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她因此成为格莱美奖历史上第三年轻的获奖者，也是最年轻的新西兰获奖者，同时她还是历史上最年轻的获得“年度制作”提名的独唱艺人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/2013-grammy-snubs-surprises-045128205.html|title=2014 Grammy Snubs, Scores & Surprises|publisher=Yahoo Music|date=2013-12-06|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417123210/https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/2013-grammy-snubs-surprises-045128205.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/9654528/Lorde-wins-a-Grammy|title=Lorde takes home two Grammys|work=Stuff.co.nz|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930035959/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/music/9654528/Lorde-wins-a-Grammy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/jan/27/daft-punk-lorde-2014-grammy-awards|title=Daft Punk and Lorde win top honours at 2014 Grammy awards|work=The Guardian|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111093127/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/jan/27/daft-punk-lorde-2014-grammy-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后在2018年的[[第60届格莱美奖|第60届格莱美奖]]中，她又因《狂想曲》获得一项年度专辑的提名。<ref name="60thGrammyNom"/>
